T02TD3555E:190a-1: badzra b'i na sva ra sva t'i s'a dha nam /
T02TD3555E:190a-3: rdo rje pi wang dbyangs can ma'i sgrub thabs /
T02TD3555E:190a-4: rdo rje dbyangs can ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD3555E:190a-5: dang por chos zhabs la btud nas //
T02TD3555E:190a-6: shes rab de nyid nyer ston pa'i //
T02TD3555E:190a-8: dbyangs can ma 'dir bshad par bya //
T02TD3555E:190a-9: gang zhig bde ba'i stan la gnas //
T02TD3555E:190a-10: stong nyid rnal 'byor bsgom par bya //
T02TD3555E:190a-11: sa bon chu skyes de bzhin du //
T02TD3555E:190a-12: bdun pa'i gnyis pa la gnas pa'i //
T02TD3555E:190a-13: brgyad pa yi ni bzhi pa las //
T02TD3555E:190a-14: dang po yi ni bzhi pas brgyan //
T02TD3555E:190a-15: de la thig le dang bcas pa //
T02TD3555E:190a-16: de las byung ba'i dbyangs can ma //
T02TD3555E:190b-0: pi wang sgrogs @190b shing de bzhin tu //
T02TD3555E:190b-1: zla ba dkar po'i 'od gsal la //
T02TD3555E:190b-2: rgyan rnams kun gyis rnam par brgyan //
T02TD3555E:190b-3: nges bzhugs lha mo chen mo ni //
T02TD3555E:190b-4: 'phel byed kyi gnas bsam par bya //
T02TD3555E:190b-5: dang po'i yi ge las skyes pa'i //
T02TD3555E:190b-6: 'khor lor rtsibs brgyad kyis brgyan pa //
T02TD3555E:190b-7: de dbus zla ba la gnas pa //
T02TD3555E:190b-8: de yi sa bon brtan bar bsam //
T02TD3555E:190b-9: de las de yi 'od zer gyis //
T02TD3555E:190b-10: bdag gi lus 'di snang bar mdzad //
T02TD3555E:190b-11: de nas ba spu'i khung nas ni //
T02TD3555E:190b-12: 'thon gyur srid pa ma lus pa'i //
T02TD3555E:190b-13: mi shes rab rib bcom nas ni //
T02TD3555E:190b-14: slar yang rang nyid la zhugs te //
T02TD3555E:190b-15: lnga pa'i 'og nas drug pa yi //
T02TD3555E:190b-16: dbyangs la thig le gnyis kyis brgyan //
T02TD3555E:190b-17: aa a'i sngon bzhin au dang aee //
T02TD3555E:190b-18: aom dang aa:yis nye bar mtshon /
T02TD3555E:190b-19: snying ga spyi bo'i gtsug dang ni //
T02TD3555E:190b-20: mgrin pa mig dang phrag pa la //
T02TD3555E:190b-21: cho ga 'di yis bkod nas ni //
T02TD3555E:190b-22: 'di yis tshangs bar spyad par bya //
T02TD3555E:190b-24: mun chen snying la gnas pa la //
T02TD3555E:190b-25: mi g-yo rang gi sa bon la //
T02TD3555E:190b-26: blo dang ldan pas brtan par bsgom //
T02TD3555E:190b-27: de nas 'bum du bzlas par bya //
T02TD3555E:190b-28: bdun gyi grangs dang ldan pa yis //
T02TD3555E:190b-29: rnam spyod rab tu dangs pa yis //
T02TD3555E:190b-30: thugs kar lha mo dbyangs can ma //
T02TD3555E:190b-31: tshigs bcad rkyang pa ma lus pa'i /
T02TD3555E:190b-32: rang bzhin gnyis pa ngag dbang bzhin //
T02TD3555E:190b-33: sngon ma mthong ba shes par 'gyur //
T02TD3555E:190b-34: sngags sogs kun gyi ngag rang bzhin //
T02TD3555E:190b-36: de don lo phyed bsten pas 'phel //
T02TD3555E:190b-37: sten byed rta dbyangs dang mtshungs pa /
T02TD3555E:190b-38: yun mi ring bas ster bar byed //
T02TD3555E:190b-39: rdo rje pi wang dbyangs can ma'i sgrub thabs rdzogs so//
